* {{audio|En-us-accompaniment.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{context|music|lang=en}} A part, usually performed by instruments, that gives support or adds to the background in music, or adds for ornamentation; also, the harmony of a figured bass.
# That which accompanies; something that attends as a circumstance, or which is added to give greater completeness to the principal thing, or by way of ornament, or for the sake of symmetry.

